<sect1 id="dir_e700b0aeb2d441d3f82dcadb30dbf1e2_1autotoc_md263">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::policy</title><para>Spawn rules, conditions, and amount providers.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_e700b0aeb2d441d3f82dcadb30dbf1e2_1autotoc_md264">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the policy layer for the spawn system. It defines rules that combine conditions (when to spawn) with amount providers (how many to spawn).</para>
</sect1>
